caption.title: Two-strain model: (a) the annual cumulative incidence for humans and (b) cumulative number of infectious mosquitoes are compared corresponding to θ = 0 (top), θ = 0.005 (second row), θ = 0.01 (third row), and θ = 0.02 (bottom) over 50 years depending on u = 0 (black), 0.5 (blue), 0.9 (red) to control the inflow rate of travelers.
caption.p: The climate data is based on the RCP 8.5 scenario.
